### SEM ################################################## 
# Mesh configuration           
# (macromesh.dat)                                
# Parameters values need to be after the 15th column        
# after the `=` signs                           
#                                                         
# The couronnes (shell) are ordered from the Earth center     
# There is (ncour + 1) interfaces :                        
#                                                         
# ----------------- interface (icour + 1)                 
#  couronne icour                                         
# ----------------- interface (icour)                     
#                                                         
# `nelh1`` and `degh1` describe the first shell (couronne)     
# The `nelh` and `degh` of the upper shells are imposed  
# by the nature of the interfaces (conform or not conform)           
#                                                         
# See domaine.f90 for more detail       
#                    
#                                                         
# To run the program on nproc processes enter :                        
# nproc   npro  square_npro                               
#                                                         
# 4       2     T                                         
# 8       2     F                                         
# 16      4     T                                         
# 32      4     F                                         
#########################################################
npro          =4
square_npro   =.false.
nregion       =6                            
parametrique  =.false.                      
ncour         =3
